name: OhShape
summary:
🕺 Dance to the rhythm of your own songs! 🕺

OhShape is the most unique VR rhythm game you can find! With more than 40 songs and different difficulty modes for every level of skill, OhShape will make you the master of the dancefloor. Do you want more content? Then you can create infinite maps with our free level editor! Download it for PC and enjoy creating your own choreagraphies to the rhythm of your songs with an easy and intuitive interface!
